        </h2>
        
        <div className="space-y-6 text-silver leading-relaxed text-lg">
          <p>
            They say the trenches swallow hype. NIGLET didn't hype — it shimmered.
          </p>
          <p>
            Forged under pressure and polished by chaos, NIGLET is the 1/1 relic that crawled out of the dirt wearing a chrome frame.
          </p>
          <p>
